# ⚠️ Email Configuration (IMPORTANT - This is required for emails to work!)
# For Gmail: You MUST use an app-specific password, NOT your regular Gmail password
# Step-by-step setup:
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Google Account: https://myaccount.google.com/security
# 2. Generate App-specific password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Select "Mail" and "Windows Computer" (or your device)
# 4. Copy the 16-character password generated
# 5. Paste it below in MAIL_PASSWORD (remove spaces)
# 6. Put your full Gmail address in MAIL_USERNAME (e.g., yourname@gmail.com)
